OL,3,CCouncil workers face industrial action
OL,4,Cballot after pay offer rejected
OL,6,FLocal authority workers are to be
OL,7,Fballoted for industrial action after
OL,8,Frejecting a pay offer.
OL,10,FMembers of Unite, employed by local
OL,11,Fauthorities in England, Wales and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland, voted by 85% against
OL,13,Fthe offer which the union said was
OL,14,Fworth #1,290 plus 2.5% on allowances.
OL,16,FThe workers include refuse collection,
OL,17,Fhousing workers and care staff.
